<div class="app-card-container about-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    
    <hr>

    <div class="row about-me-box">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "joe-pic.png", width: 300, alt: "profile image"%>
        <div class="skills-container">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="inner-skill">
              <h5><%= skill.title %><h5>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8 about-paragraph">
        <p>I've been building things my entire life - from construction projects, plumbing repairs, to websites and web applications. It's what I enjoy doing. I now build products to help businesses deliver information as a Full Stack Developer. With experience in Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, React and Redux, I've built social platforms focused on community-empowerment, architectured web applications, and created multi page websites to help businesses deliver information.
        </p>
        <p> Have a project in mind? Interested to learn more about me? <br> Lets talk! </p>
        
          <%# <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button> %>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <%# <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div> %>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Flatiron School 2018-2019
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Northern Virginia Community College - major: computer science 2017-2018
            </div>
            <%# <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div> %>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


